column5: I dont do drugs just so you all know. I just have alot of fun fishing.
You have too much fun Brian
medication is drugs too you know just  saying.....   lol  just kidding  nothing like having fun
cool have fun. enjoy what you have today. tommorows never an option.
I dont do drugs just so you all know. I just have alot of fun fishing.    I hear enough Terry is like Meth

Lmao. That's funny!!!!  I think about bringing my Bose speaker in the boat but I am always so focused. Maybe I should make fishing a little more fun!!!  Also I think my girlfriend bailed on me for tomorrow morning so it looks like I am solo again tomorrow.  I will stay clear of any rocking out toons on the lake.
Doin' a jig while you jig. Why not ! Thanks for sharing Brian.

Rhythm is a terrible thing to waste! Luckily for you, you didn't have much to start with! LOL Looks like fun B! Funny enough, that song is on my list to learn for the coming bar season! Did yah catch any fish? HH
Terry and I can sing it for you if you like.  http://ontariofishingcommunity.com/forums/index.php?showtopic=75637     YUUUPPPPP         Right on.
I'm picturing a double-loaded beer helmet above those legs.
I'm picturing a double-loaded beer helmet above those legs.  Are you kidding. That sun would have them piss warm in no time. YUKKKK I keep them in the fridge,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,AT HOME.
That is cute! And the music is an African band...the Congos I think!
That is cute! And the music is an African band...the Congos I think!  Yes,south African. All 4 are brothers. Kongos.  I thought they were Newfies at first. LOL
